    npx:hasSignature "XgtXjotWSih/Hhr3ez7dRI/mKr68jdP62heXYLDVT/orfWovm8YV6HoYzCsQ+TCUbqZEx2Yo9x/jJ3KsjJobeosmY/g+UTI3GxQzrtuq3+ac4RCGdxKN1/9c3eb6w58cEzkroN/p+U8E/dnRaQ2tRJpbmW72DHsvh5OAyjmZ5gM=";
    npx:hasSignatureTarget this:;
